Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. MacPhail's chosen the Ser Veresta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you obey me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect of you, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I trust you,\NI'd like to ask a favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:16.93,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Holiday for Two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia? I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... so you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a spacious room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one of the perks of\Nbeing student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not for being\Nstudent council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it's a fringe benefit\Nfor top-tier students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you make your way up the rankings\Nand become a Page One,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be privy to private\Nrooms such as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're a Page One, too, Claudia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a sad thing to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you could take\Na bit more interest in me, Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, compared to that, being student council\Npresident brings nothing but hassle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it's far less fulfilling\Nthan you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you take on the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am fond of hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So your summoning me here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,does that have something to do\Nwith that hassle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness,\NI don't need to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These students were entered\Nin the next Phoenix Festa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but they've been forced to withdraw from\Ncompetition in the last few weeks due to injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The causes are many,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were attacked by somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like in Julis's case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's highly likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, at the moment, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the Disciplinary Committee\Nand I have strong suspicions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,against Lester MacPhail\Nand Randy Hooke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being that neither of them have an alibi\Nfor the time of the attack yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But with no proof, that leaves\Nyour hands tied, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we do have one sure advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that we know\Nwho'll be targeted next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that brings me\Nto the favor I mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, would you\Nmind staying by Julis's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because the next time\Nshe comes under attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she might not necessarily\Nbe able to handle it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason why it has to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, that girl has a tendency\Nto distance herself from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, however, she appears\Nto be comfortable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is going to show me around\Nthe city on our next day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are oblivious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, if you don't mind my asking,\Nwhy are you so concerned about Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What student council president wouldn't\Ntry to protect a student at her own school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like the other students, I have come here\Nto do "what it is I'm supposed to do."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm only doing what\NI need to do towards that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I can't ask for a favor\Nwithout offering a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Claudia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're here, you might\Nas well desire me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do help yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hold up a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! So anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're all set, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you're supposed to do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you standing there\Nwith your mouth wide open?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean... It's just that\Nyou look so different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! But you really look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You moron! Are you\Ntrying to embarrass me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, this is just\Na makeshift outfit I threw together
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from some clothes\Nthey sent me from my country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the main stage,\Nthe largest in Asterisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Festa finals are held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from this one, there are three\Nlarge-scale stages, seven mid-sized stages,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and as far as smaller outdoor stages go,\Nthere are too many too count.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know there were that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since it's considered etiquette\Nto use the stages for duels in the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that many people adhere\Nto those rules, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there are duels right in the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to live in a town like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do you want to grab\Nsome lunch around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, can we have lunch here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure you want to eat here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, definitely here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a princess, Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, princesses don't normally\Ngo to burger joints, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's called a bias.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's an actual example\Nright in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about this place from my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even I have friends, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not here... but in my\Nown country, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis, can we talk about\Nsomething serious for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About that attack on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I talked about it with Claudia, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I don't think you should\Nbe going out alone, or dueling...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to alter my\Nroutine because of such cowards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one to decide my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My will belongs to me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well! Always\Nthe heroine, aren't you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Despite getting targeted\Nby a mystery attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eavesdropping? Such impeccable taste, Lester.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone worthy of being\Nmy opponent, I'll just take him on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you take me on\Nright here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to repeat this until\Nit registers? I have no inclination to take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, I'm\Ntelling you to battle me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you've\Ntaken it far enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard\Nhow Julis was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you pick a fight here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,too bad if people lump you in\Nwith the cowards from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that I'm no different\Nthan guys who sneak around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll be happy\Nto start by annihilating you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You call me a coward, and\Nyou're making a run for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You damned wuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take part in a meaningless duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody knows that you've always\Ntaken out your opponents fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for a chance to duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never do anything\Ncowardly like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to let you off easy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought,\Nyou really are a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, skip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got ketchup on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're\Nunfathomable, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot, and it was fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it? I-I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the risk of repeating myself,\Nall I did was repay my debt, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are students from\NLe Wolfe Black Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're getting into it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's the first blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a common ploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They surround their target\Nby feigning a brawl,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then go to town on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that it was Le Wolfe\Nwho went after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show them the money, and hoodlums\Nlike these will take on just about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This would be a clear-cut\Ncase of self-defense, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to grill some\Nanswers out of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give him a break and keep it\Nto medium rare or so, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't even much of a warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I'll burn off that bizarre\Nhairstyle of yours, roots and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be succinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you the order to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some guy I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd pay us\Nto make you guys hurt a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did this guy look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was dressed all in black.\NA tall, burly guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who hired us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Come back here!\N- Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't chase him too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just barely, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My clothes are shredded, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that was a bit careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you could've evaded\Nan attack like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You even got your Lux demolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, that's\Nabout all I can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So dealing with multiple\Nopponents isn't your thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Security should be showing up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we withdraw, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still have some time after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I hate how that's become\Nlike, second nature to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's get this over with, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take off your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... J-J-J-J-Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry it up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-G-Get your mind out of the gutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that! I'm offering\Nto repair your ripped clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Repair? You mean you can sew, Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my forte...\Nbut well, I'm not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just as responsible\Nfor this, too, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wish to incur\Nany more debt from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's the deal, fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this another thing\Nyou learned from your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a feeling, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Julis. By any chance,\Nthese friends of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why, you! Who said\Nyou could look at that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girl in the middle. That's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The people in this photograph\Nare, without question, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but as a child,\NI was a tomboy, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would often sneak out of\Nthe palace without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I lost my way in the slums,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and got dragged into an alley\Nby a group of vulgar thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There I was, helpless...\Nunable to do anything but sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then who appeared before me\Nand came to my rescue were those girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I returned to the palace, I learned that\Nthey were from the orphanage in the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I started sneaking out of\Nthe palace to follow them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did those girls know\Nthat you were a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, because at the time\NI kept that from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure the nuns knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That orphanage had been built with the funds\Ncreated by my mother, but those funds have run dry,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it's getting harder and harder\Nto keep it running every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What today's children need\Nmore than anything... sadly, it's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but Julis, you're\Nthe princess of your country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there some\Nother way to raise money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd have any money at my disposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, in a puppet regime of\Nthe Integrated Empire Foundation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could never secure approval for\Na welfare project with no hope of revenues!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, what else\Ncan I do but raise it myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, I had my skills as a Strega,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:18:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and what better title for a freak\Nthan my standing as a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a vulgar and insignificant city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They make students battle each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the whole world\Ncan't get enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their greed is a maelstrom, sucking in\Neverything around it until it's horribly engorged,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it will continue to grow unchecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's precisely why it's\Nthe city closest to all desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will obtain what I want here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not because someone asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For my own sake, I will do\Nwhatever I want right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my reason for going into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now take this and go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can call it even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is something my friends from\Nthe orphanage gave me for my birthday years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They all took turns embroidering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this especially heinous part\Nwas done by my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving already, Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to take care of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's gone back\Nto her old ways for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, she was just\Nbeginning to thaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, the princess was\Nreading a letter from somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now she's run off\Nwith an ashen face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That might not be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her opponent is that\Nguy who shot at her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nwhy didn't she tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she doesn't trust me after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it was quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all that girl can do to protect\Nwhat she has in her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, she counts you\Nas one of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis... protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I'm supposed to do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is protect you, Ayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then... Then I'm going to\Nprotect you, too, Big Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That will be my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get it at the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Sister's sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What it is that I'm supposed to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was you who taught me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To protect Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm supposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato and the Ser Veresta...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see how far they'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, to think that Ayato would be in such a panic\Nthat he'd leap from such a high place...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4 - Unshackled
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do feel a bit jealous.
